msgid "All bookmarks"
msgstr "全部书签"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:37
msgid "Unread bookmarks"
msgstr "未读书签"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:40
msgid "Public shared bookmarks"
msgstr "已公开分享书签"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:41
msgid "This public feed does not include an authentication token and only shows bookmarks from users who explicitly enabled public sharing."
msgstr "这个公开订阅源不包含认证令牌，只会显示明确启用了公开分享的用户所分享的书签。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:44
msgid "All URLs support the following URL parameters:"
msgstr "所有链接都支持以下 URL 参数："

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:46
msgid "specifies the maximum number of bookmarks in the feed. The default is 100."
msgstr "指定订阅源中书签数量的最大值，默认值为 100。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:47
msgid "specifies the search query. You can copy an example from the bookmark list URL after running a search."
msgstr "指定搜索语句。你可以在书签列表执行搜索后，从浏览器地址栏复制一个示例。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:48
msgid "filters unread or read bookmarks. Use yes for unread and no for read."
msgstr "筛选未读或已读书签。使用 yes 表示未读，no 表示已读。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:49
msgid "filters shared or unshared bookmarks. Use yes for shared and no for unshared."
msgstr "筛选已分享或未分享书签。使用 yes 表示已分享，no 表示未分享。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:52
msgid "Please note that these URLs include an authentication token and should be handled like any other credential."
msgstr "请注意，这些链接包含认证令牌，应像其他凭据一样妥善保管。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:53
msgid "Anyone with access to these URLs can read all your bookmarks."
msgstr "任何持有这些链接的人都可以读取你的全部书签。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:54
msgid "If you think a feed URL was compromised, delete the feed token in the"
msgstr "如果你认为订阅链接可能已经泄露，请在"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:56
msgid "After deleting the token, reload this page to generate new feed URLs."
msgstr "删除令牌后，刷新本页即可生成新的订阅链接。"

